A chair crafted within the Phantom Forest, complete with...ornaments...from unlucky travelers. Recovers 50 HP and 50 MP every 10 seconds.
A chair made out of Ice Queen's ice pieces. Sit on it to recover HP 40 and MP 30 per 10 seconds.
Mr. Oh sells these rare spices at the Maple 7th Day Market. You can sell them to Abdula for a profit.
You can find these memorabilia from Thailand at the Maple 7th Day Market. You can sell them to Abdula for a profit.
Lena sells delicious unagi at the Maple  7th Day Market. You can sell it to Abdula for a profit.

A comfortable, stylish seat that only forms when true love exists between two people.  Recovers 45 HP, 45 MP every 10 seconds.

Inferno will comfort your body. Recovers 60 HP every 10 seconds.
Abyss will comfort your mind. Recovers 60 MP every 10 seconds.
The chair in which the chiefs of the Miwok tribe sat. If you sit in this chair, you can receive the strength of the Miwok ancestors and recover 65MP in 10 seconds.
A small candle given by Cassandra. This candle will turn off automatically when the game ends.
You will recover 50 HP every 10 seconds. Perhaps, as you recline, you will find the answer to many of life's questions.
You will recover 50 HP every 10 seconds. You will experience the might of a conqueror after recovery.
A chair makes you feel like you're sitting in the lap of luxury. Also recovers 50 HP every 10 seconds.
A white chair created to celebrate Maple Story's 6th Anniversary. Sit on it to restore 35 HP and 10 MP every 10 seconds.
A chair that restores HP every 10 seconds when used. It's very strong since it was made from bamboo grown on Rien.
A pretty cushion shaped like a moon. Recovers 60 HP every 10 seconds.
60 HP is restored every 10 seconds if you lean back on this cute Male Desert Rabbit Cushion.
A pink beach chair that makes you want to go to the beach. Restores 60 HP every 10 seconds.
A luxurious velvet sofa dyed with a beautiful shade of navy. Restores 60 HP every 10 seconds.
A designer chair that glows with a passionate red. Restores 60 HP every 10 seconds.
A Giant Star that Cassandra made for you. If you hold it during the Starlight Festival, you can receive 1 Star Stamp every hour. \n#cDisappears when you log out of the game.

A Maple Leaf that signifies Maple Story's 6 year journey. Something good will happen if you hold onto it for 1 hour.
An unknown being that has yet to be explained.
When you sit on the Halloween Broomstick Chair, 50 MP is restored every 10 seconds
When you rest on the Shinsoo, 50 HP and 50 MP are restored every 10 seconds
An eerie looking chair that resembles Olivia. Recovers 40 HP and 35 MP every 10 seconds
A new chair to recline and relax in throughout the Thanksgiving holiday.\nRecovers 60 HP and 30 MP every 10 seconds.
A new chair that makes you feel like a Rock Star.\nRecovers 60 HP and 30 MP every 10 seconds.
A solid ice crystal that contains Maha Charm. Hold onto it for one hour and the crystal will melt, enabling you to acquire the Charm.
A charm that contains protection from Maha, the spirit of Polearm. Take this to Cassandra for a chance to answer questions and receive prizes.
A huge X-mas Gift Box big enough to fit a grownup. It has a message that reads, "I am here for you." Sitting in it will recover 50 HP and MP every 10 seconds.
A cushion that resembles Pink Bean, the underling of the Black Mage. Leaning against the cushion and resting will recover 50 HP and 30 MP every 10 seconds.
Cuddling with the Polar Bear for some cozy, comfy rest will recover 50 HP and 50 MP every 10 seconds.
Snuggle up with Aran's loyal mount, Ryko, to recover 50 HP and MP every 10 seconds.
Lean back on this imposing Tiger Skin Chair to restore 50 HP and 30 MP every 10 seconds.
There is a swing on the Persimmon Tree with ripe persimmons.

Sink yourself into this heavenly cake chair next to someone else who owns it as well, and watch it create a scrumptious effect! Mmm, this chair is so delicious you'll recover 50 HP every 10 seconds.
Yummy! Use this chair next to someone else who's also using it, and a mouth-watering chocolate fondue appears. Smack your lips and dream about treats as you recover 50 HP every 10 seconds.
Perch yourself on the hand of this powerful yellow robot to recover 50 HP and 30 MP every 10 seconds.
